{{Wikipedia how to}}

Some editors find accessdates distracting. To hide the accessdate, edit [[Special:MyPage/common.css]]:

<syntaxhighlight lang="css">
span.reference-accessdate {
display: none;
}
</syntaxhighlight>


To show a smaller access date:
<syntaxhighlight lang="css">
span.reference-accessdate {
font-size:80%
}
</syntaxhighlight>

